text: Independent's Day is the third studio album by American rapper Royce da 5'9", released on June 28, 2005 through M.I.C Records. The album was not as successful as his first two albums. The lead single of this album was "Independent's Day". The album has many guest features including Cee Lo Green and Kid Vishis and Sarah Stokes. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2005 albums Category:Royce da 5'9" albums
title: Independent's Day
